dex": 198, "start": 809070, "end": 811950}, {"text": ["Do I have to remind you", "that I'm the commander of"], "index": 199, "start": 811950, "end": 814483}, {"text": ["the Autozam fleet that's", "here to invade Cephiro?"], "index": 200, "start": 814507, "end": 817040}, {"text": ["What made you decide", "to come here all alone?"], "index": 201, "start": 818000, "end": 820800}, {"text": ["I wanted to apologize\u2026 to the", "person who really loves Lantis."], "index": 202, "start": 821050, "end": 825170}, {"text": ["I thought that you really cared", "for Lantis, Eagle\u2026 So I came here\u2026"], "index": 203, "start": 826220, "end": 831430}, {"text": ["[Cries softly]"], "index": 204, "start": 831720, "end": 835230}, {"text": ["If I tried to comfort you", "right now, I hope that"], "index": 205, "start": 835810, "end": 839258}, {"text": ["the people who love", "you won't think it's a trick."], "index": 206, "start": 839282, "end": 842730}, {"text": ["[Cries softly]"], "index": 207, "start": 843070, "end": 845900}, {"text": ["[Sobs miserably]"], "index": 208, "start": 845900, "end": 854540}, {"text": ["I'm so sorry!"], "index": 209, "start": 854540, "end": 856080}, {"text": ["I know I'm your enemy, but I", "just can't come to hate you, Eagle!"], "index": 210, "start": 856870, "end": 861750}, {"text": ["You were so kind to", "me on the battleship."], "index": 211, "start": 862670, "end": 865670}, {"text": ["How you saved Lantis", "during the battle with Nova."], "index": 212, "start": 866260, "end": 869510}, {"text": ["I just can't forget about that!"], "index": 213, "start": 870090, "end": 872300}, {"text": ["- [Sobs miserably]", "- Neither can I..."], "index": 214, "start": 872300, "end": 875180}, {"text": ["Master Mage Clef. Presea."], "index": 215, "start": 881560, "end": 884110}, {"text": ["[Thunder booms] [Deep rumbling]"], "index": 216, "start": 884480, "end": 893120}, {"text": ["[Panicked screams]"], "index": 217, "start": 893120, "end": 901710}, {"text": ["[Panicked shout]", "Lantis, save me!"], "index": 218, "start": 901710, "end": 905250}, {"text": ["Huh?"], "index": 219, "start": 906090, "end": 907670}, {"text": ["Are you protecting me?"], "index": 220, "start": 908380, "end": 910300}, {"text": ["Puu! Puu!"], "index": 221, "start": 910300, "end": 911470}, {"text": ["[Giggles] It's must be", "because you think I'm so cute!"], "index": 222, "start": 911470, "end": 914970}, {"text": ["[Annoyed puu-ing]", "[alarmed shout]"], "index": 223, "start": 914970, "end": 917640}, {"text": ["I hope Hikaru and the", "others are doing all right."], "index": 224, "start": 918100, "end": 921770}, {"text": ["I hope they're not hurt."], "index": 225, "start": 921770, "end": 923190}, {"text": ["They're all right, Mira! No one can", "beat the legendary Magic Knights!"], "index": 226, "start": 923190, "end": 926820}, {"text": ["Mm-hmm!"], "index": 227, "start": 926820, "end": 928530}, {"text": ["I wish we could be as strong as", "them so we wouldn't be scared right now."], "index": 228, "start": 928530, "end": 932820}, {"text": ["Puu puu!"], "index": 229, "start": 933910, "end": 935330}, {"text": ["[Reassuring puus]"], "index": 230, "start": 936290, "end": 939960}, {"text": ["[Strained shouts]"], "index": 231, "start": 939960, "end": 942790}, {"text": ["Caldina!"], "index": 232, "start": 942790, "end": 944380}, {"text": ["[Panting] What's going on?"], "index": 233, "start": 945880, "end": 949010}, {"text": ["[Thunder booms]"], "index": 234, "start": 949970, "end": 952840}, {"text": ["Is the crumbling of Cephiro", "reaching its final stages?"], "index": 235, "start": 952840, "end": 955970}, {"text": ["[Alarmed shouts] [Deep rumbling]"], "index": 236, "start": 956310, "end": 959020}, {"text": ["Umi!"], "index": 237, "start": 959350, "end": 960850}, {"text": ["Hold on Ascot!"], "index": 238, "start": 960850, "end": 962600}, {"text": ["[Startled gasp["], "index": 239, "start": 962600, "end": 964360}, {"text": ["Ascot, it's hard for me to say", "this, but Umi's in love with..."], "index": 240, "start": 964360, "end": 967860}, {"text": ["It's alright."], "index": 241, "start": 969820, "end": 971030}, {"text": ["Huh?"], "index": 242, "start": 971030, "end": 972280}, {"text": ["I love Umi."], "index": 243, "start": 973860, "end": 975370}, {"text": ["That's what my", "heart honestly says."], "index": 244, "start": 975870, "end": 977910}, {"text": ["And even if Umi doesn't love", "me... even if she thinks poorly of me..."], "index": 245, "start": 978620, "end": 982250}, {"text": ["It won't matter to me. I can be", "happy knowing I love her, right?"], "index": 246, "start": 983960, "end": 988420}, {"text": ["Oh, Ascot."], "index": 247, "start": 990130, "end": 991590}, {"text": ["I'm going to look for", "Umi and the others."], "index": 248, "start": 992130, "end": 994510}, {"text": ["Alright! Give it all", "you've got and go find her!"], "index": 249, "start": 994890, "end": 998470}, {"text": ["Ascot has become a fine adult."], "index": 250, "start": 1000680, "end": 1003440}, {"text": ["He sure has. I'm happy but", "kinda sad too. It's a weird feelin'."], "index": 251, "start": 1003640, "end": 1008070}, {"text": ["Don't cry."], "index": 252, "start": 1011530, "end": 1012900}, {"text": ["You'll make Lantis sad too", "if you keep crying, Hikaru."], "index": 253, "start": 1014490, "end": 1017910}, {"text": ["I'm sure Lantis must hate", "me for doing what I did."], "index": 254, "start": 1018700, "end": 1022790}, {"text": ["For doing what I", "did to his brother."], "index": 255, "start": 1022790, "end": 1025540}, {"text": ["I know he can't", "possibly love me!"], "index": 256, "start": 1025540, "end": 1028540}, {"text": ["But I love him, Eagle!"], "index": 257, "start": 1028540, "end": 1030210}, {"text": ["I don't know why, but I do."], "index": 258, "start": 1030210, "end": 1032260}, {"text": ["If you know why you love", "someone, then it isn't real love at all."], "index": 259, "start": 1038510, "end": 1042980}, {"text": ["Huh?"], "index": 260, "start": 1042980, "end": 1044270}, {"text": ["You don't know why\u2026"], "index": 261, "start": 1044270, "end": 1045980}, {"text": ["\u2026but you love him, right?"], "index": 262, "start": 1046310, "end": 1048440}, {"text": ["Mm-hmm."], "index": 263, "start": 1048440, "end": 1050440}, {"text": ["I'm sure that the last", "Pillar, Princess Emeraude,"], "index": 264, "start": 1050820, "end": 1053990}, {"text": ["probably thought the same", "thing that you're thinking right now."], "index": 265, "start": 1053990, "end": 1057240}, {"text": ["She must have asked herself..."], "index": 266, "start": 1057240, "end": 1059160}, {"text": ["\"Why? Why have I fallen", "in love with someone?\""], "index": 267, "start": 1059160, "end": 1062370}, {"text": ["She probably wondered why", "she couldn't stop her own heart."], "index": 268, "start": 1062370, "end": 1066040}, {"text": ["I'm sure that she wasn't able to", "come up with an answer to that question."], "index": 269, "start": 1066420, "end": 1071670}, {"text": ["But still\u2026 she fell in", "love with Zagato..."], "index": 270, "start": 1072250, "end": 1075470}, {"text": ["Every person has feelings that they", "can't control that are a part of them."], "index": 271, "start": 1077050, "end": 1081680}, {"text": ["People always worry about", "the feelings they can't control."], "index": 272, "start": 1082640, "end": 1086730}, {"text": ["I myself have felt that if I could, I'd", "like to be friends with you, my enemy."], "index": 273, "start": 1088020, "end": 1094190}, {"text": ["And Lantis, too?"], "index": 274, "start": 1094530, "end": 1096110}, {"text": ["Lantis, too."], "index": 275, "start": 1096650, "end": 1098200}, {"text": ["But I truly love Autozam."], "index": 276, "start": 1098450, "end": 1100490}, {"text": ["I want to be able", "to save my people."], "index": 277, "start": 1100700, "end": 1102990}, {"text": ["But I...I couldn't forget of my", "true wish\u2026no matter what I did."], "index": 278, "start": 1103580, "end": 1109120}, {"text": ["What do you mean \"true wish\"?"], "index": 279, "start": 1110500, "end": 1112380}, {"text": ["- [Hacking cough]", "- Eagle! Eagle, what's the matter!?"], "index": 280, "start": 1114000, "end": 1120510}, {"text": ["Eagle!"], "index": 281, "start": 1121300, "end": 1122510}, {"text": ["Eagle, are you okay!?"], "index": 282, "start": 1122510, "end": 1124810}, {"text": ["Please don't worry, Hikaru..."], "index": 283, "start": 1126310, "end": 1127980}, {"text": ["But I'm sure that", "it's impossible not to."], "index": 284, "start": 1128440, "end": 1131110}, {"text": ["Eagle..."], "index": 285, "start": 1131690, "end": 1133110}, {"text": ["Alcyone, you", "have got to tell us..."], "index": 286, "start": 1138650, "end": 1140860}, {"text": ["Where is the location of Debonair,", "the being who controlled you?"], "index": 287, "start": 1140860, "end": 1144280}, {"text": ["[Startled gasp]"], "index": 288, "start": 1144700, "end": 1146160}, {"text": ["Lantis, Zagato's younger brother, was", "captured by one of Debonair's people."], "index": 289, "start": 1147450, "end": 1151750}, {"text": ["We have to rescue him quickly!"], "index": 290, "start": 1152330, "end": 1154250}, {"text": ["Lord Zagato's younger brother?"], "index": 291, "start": 1155840, "end": 1158590}, {"text": ["If this continues, Cephiro", "will crumble completely!"], "index": 292, "start": 1159220, "end": 1162970}, {"text": ["So Alcyone, please", "tell me where she is."], "index": 293, "start": 1163550, "end": 1166810}, {"text": ["Now that it's a world without", "my Lord Zagato, I no longer care."], "index": 294, "start": 1167390, "end": 1172440}, {"text": ["[Startled gasp] [Thunder booms]"], "index": 295, "start": 1172770, "end": 1174900}, {"text": ["The man I risked", "everything for... including"], "index": 296, "start": 1175270, "end": 1178553}, {"text": ["betraying you, my", "master... is no longer here."], "index": 297, "start": 1178577, "end": 1181860}, {"text": ["Why was I allowed to survive?"], "index": 298, "start": 1185370, "end": 1188080}, {"text": ["[Sobs miserably] Even if", "he didn't return my love\u2026"], "index": 299, "start": 1188580, "end": 1193130}, {"text": ["...I wanted to die with", "him, at the very least."], "index": 300, "start": 1193920, "end": 1197130}, {"text": ["- [Heartbroken sobs]", "- Oh, poor Alcyone."], "index": 301, "start": 1197130, "end": 1204180}, {"text": ["Eagle, are you sick?"], "index": 302, "start": 1206100, "end": 1208770}, {"text": ["Does Lantis know", "anything about this?"], "index": 303, "start": 1208970, "end": 1211810}, {"text": ["I absolutely don't want", "him... to ever know about this."], "index": 304, "start": 1212100, "end": 1216770}, {"text": ["[Speechless sigh]"], "index": 305, "start": 1217230, "end": 1219320}, {"text": ["I don't... have any time left..."], "index": 306, "start": 1221240, "end": 1224360}, {"text": ["Either you or me."], "index": 307, "start": 1225320, "end": 1227490}, {"text": ["One of us seems to be the", "one... that can become the Pillar..."], "index": 308, "start": 1228660, "end": 1232460}, {"text": ["Huh?"], "index": 309, "start": 1232460, "end": 1233790}, {"text": ["We should... make it", "clear... [Shallow breath]"], "index": 310, "start": 1233920, "end": 1238090}, {"text": ["I can't let Autozam", "wither away as it is now."], "index": 311, "start": 1238340, "end": 1241840}, {"text": ["However I'm sure you don't want Cephiro", "to crumble away like this either."], "index": 312, "start": 1242930, "end": 1248810}, {"text": ["Mmm..."], "index": 313, "start": 1249010, "end": 1250350}, {"text": ["If... I have the qualifications", "to become the Pillar\u2026"], "index": 314, "start": 1250970, "end": 1255650}, {"text": ["I'll stay in Cephiro..."], "index": 315, "start": 1256190, "end": 1258150}, {"text": ["...as the Pillar, so I can", "prevent this world from crumbling."], "index": 316, "start": 1258520, "end": 1262440}, {"text": ["In exchange, Hikaru I'd like you", "to allow the people of Autozam"], "index": 317, "start": 1263280, "end": 1266950}, {"text": ["to enter this country peacefully so", "that they can examine the Pillar System."], "index": 318, "start": 1267240, "end": 1271620}, {"text": ["I promise... that they won't try", "to invade you if you let them in."], "index": 319, "start": 1271620, "end": 1275620}, {"text": ["You have my word."], "index": 320, "start": 1275960, "end": 1277540}, {"text": ["[Hacking cough]"], "index": 321, "start": 1279040, "end": 1282590}, {"text": ["[Deep breath] And... if you", "become the Pillar\u2026 [Heavy panting]"], "index": 322, "start": 1282590, "end": 1289720}, {"text": ["[Startled gasp]"], "index": 323, "start": 1289720, "end": 1291350}, {"text": ["What exactly do you plan to", "do with this country, Hikaru?"], "index": 324, "start": 1291350, "end": 1295600}, {"text": ["[Deep rumbling]"], "index": 325, "start": 1321090, "end": 1325090}, {"text": ["[Thunder booms]"], "index": 326, "start": 1333430, "end": 1336270}, {"text": ["Who is it today?"], "index": 327, "start": 1463150, "end": 1465190}, {"text": ["Today it's Hikaru!"], "index": 328, "start": 1468860, "end": 1470820}, {"text": ["Hey everybody! Did you", "guess right? I'll see ya later!"], "index": 329, "start": 1471490, "end": 1476910}]